{"kind":"send","message":{"method":"item/completed","params":{"completedAtMs":1781603089455,"item":{"content":[],"id":"rs_09fca0886ac2043c016a311b08fba081919539f088fdba68f9","summary":["**Writing stepwise**\n\nI’m considering how to enumerate cases using a truth table over items and their enabled status. It seems like a methodical approach, so I’ll aim to break it down step by step. I want to ensure I’m clear about what each case represents and how they interact, tracking the enabled condition properly. Let’s see how that can be structured effectively! My focus is on clarity throughout this process."],"type":"reasoning"},"threadId":"019ecfd1-8692-7d82-bf7d-17b63b109dfe","turnId":"019ecfd1-8752-7013-8bf6-e893340e5dc5"}}}
